snippet.title: Zombie Gunship Survival - Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
Download the game here: https://fgurl.net/YTZGS

SHOOT ZOMBIES. PROTECT HUMANITY.
**FOLLOW-UP TO THE #1 TOP-GROSSING SHOOTER, ZOMBIE GUNSHIP!**

Experience the power of an AC-130 aircraft and annihilate zombies in this intense shooter. With a devastating apocalypse having broken out, defend humanity from the skies while building a shelter on the ground to keep out the undead.

Follow ZGS on social media for more info & updates:
Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/ZombieGunshipSurvival/
Twitter: https://twitter.com/ZG_Survival
Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/zombiegunshipsurvival
